Package com.interzoid.sdk.model

package com.interzoid.sdk.model
Contains the model classes for the Interzoid SDK.
  • Class
    Description
    AddressMatchKeyRequest
    Represents a request for generating an address match key, used for comparing and sorting address data.
    AddressMatchKeyRequest.MatchAlgorithm
    Enumerates the available match algorithms for generating address match keys.
    Category
    The category used for generating the match key.
    CloudConnectResponse
    This is a generic response interface for the Cloud Connect services
    CloudDatabaseJsonResponse
    This represents a match report in JSON format.
    CloudDatabaseJsonResponse.MatchCluster
    This represents a match cluster in JSON format.
    CloudDatabaseStringResponse
    This is a string response message for the Cloud Database service
    CloudWorkloadRequest
    The CloudWorkloadRequest class is used to run cloud database workload requests against your cloud connected database.
    CloudWorkloadRequestValidator
    Validates the CreateTableRequest object
    CompanyNameMatchKeyRequest
    Represents a request for generating a company name match key, used for comparing and sorting company names.
    CompanyNameMatchKeyRequest.MatchAlgorithm
    Enumerates the available match algorithms for generating company name match keys.
    FullNameMatchKeyRequest
    Represents a request for generating a full name match key, used for comparing and sorting full names.
    FullNameMatchScoreRequest
    Represents a request for calculating the match score between two full names.
    InterzoidRequest
    Represents a base request class for Interzoid API requests.
    InterzoidResponse
    Represents the response structure for Interzoid API responses.
    MatchKeyResponse
    Represents the response structure for Interzoid API responses related to matching keys.
    MatchScoreResponse
    Represents the response structure for Interzoid API responses related to matching scores.
    OrganizationMatchScoreRequest
    Represents a request structure for obtaining a matching score between two organization values.
    Process
    The matching process to be executed.
    ResponseType
    Represents the response type for the MatchKey API.
    Source
    The source datasource used for generating the match keys
    TextFileMatchRequest
    This is a request object for the Delimited File Match service
    ValidCloudWorkloadRequest
    Represents a custom annotation for validating Cloud Workload API requests.
